# Reuse Shared Props

USE shared prop types from `@lib/ui/props` WHEN defining component props with common fields like `label`, `value`, `children`, `title`, `icon`, `onClick`, etc.

## Example

```tsx
// ✅ Good: Reuse shared props
import { LabelProp, ValueProp } from '@lib/ui/props'

type MyComponentProps = LabelProp & ValueProp<number>

// ❌ Bad: Duplicate prop definitions
type MyComponentProps = {
  label: ReactNode
  value: number
}
```
